  "message": "deps: bump astro 5\u21926 + starlight 0.34\u21920.38; drop stale overrides\n\nDependabot PR #1 bumped astro from 5.18.1 to 6.1.6 alone. That\nfails the docs build because:\n  - @astrojs/starlight@0.34 has peerDependencies: { astro: \"^5.5.0\" }\n  - root package.json had `overrides: { zod: \"3.25.76\",\n    \"@astrojs/sitemap\": \"3.3.0\" }` from a prior conflict that pinned\n    sitemap to 3.3.0 \u2192 which pinned zod to 3.x \u2192 which conflicts\n    with astro 6's required zod ^4.3.6\n\nFixes the bump by also:\n  - bumping @astrojs/starlight from 0.34.0 to 0.38.4 (peer: astro ^6.0.0)\n  - dropping both overrides so npm resolves zod 4.3.6 + sitemap 3.7.2\n    naturally\n\nVerified locally: clean install gives one zod (4.3.6, deduped),\ndocs build emits 13 pages, typecheck passes, integration test\nstill works. Closes Dependabot PR #1 with the same delta + the\ntwo fixes it needed to actually work.",
